    "body": "We enable deterministic mode for sm100 bwd kernel and fix outstanding race conditions.\r\n\r\nPR includes:\r\n\r\n1.  Sync compute warpgroup prior to releasing LSE (for tmem store fence) and release Psum + producer commit on dS (for tmem store fence and async smem fence); both were causing errors.\r\n2. Sync compute warpgroup (not just sync warp) after `fence_view_async_tmem_load` in loop computing dS.\r\n3. Add dq/dk/dv semaphores to interface and hook into sm100 bwd code.\r\n4. Enable SPT schedule for causal deterministic.\r\n5. Make placing dS in tmem or smem for `dK = dS.T @ Q` MMA a tuneable parameter and place in smem for causal deterministic; this is slightly faster.",
    "created_at": "2025-11-24T20:56:36Z",
    "updated_at": "2025-11-25T01:33:26Z",
    "closed_at": "2025-11-25T01:33:08Z",
